cache/generation/drafts/visuals.md:142:For inner-shadow or clipped overlay effects, combine `SetBlurRadius` with `SetCutoutPolicy`. `Dali::Ui::CutoutPolicy::CUTOUT_VIEW_WITH_CORNER_RADIUS` cuts out the view area including its corner radius, while `Dali::Ui::CutoutPolicy::CUTOUT_OUTSIDE_WITH_CORNER_RADIUS` keeps the effect inside the rounded shape.
